A basket of strawberries is a basket containing 1 to 5 strawberries. Three baskets full of strawberries is the payment for a farmer to watch over a dwellberry bush or an orange tree in the Farming skill. They can be obtained either by filling a basket or as a 1/100 drop from gourmet implings.

When eaten a strawberry heals 1-6 hitpoints (1 + 6% of the players maximum hitpoints). Up to 5 strawberries may be put in a fruit basket. A basket full of strawberries has the ability to hold 30 hitpoints of food, making it fourth to Purple sweets, Saradomin brews, and the Reward token (Gnome Restaurant) when it comes to the amount of hitpoints of food that can be held in one inventory slot.

Three baskets full of strawberries is the payment for a farmer to watch over a [[dwellberry]] bush or an [[orange tree]] in the [[Farming]] skill. They can be obtained either by filling a basket or as a 1/100 drop from [[gourmet impling]]s.

When eaten a strawberry heals 1-6 [[hitpoints]] (1 + 6% of the players maximum hitpoints). Up to 5 strawberries may be put in a fruit [[basket]]. A basket full of strawberries has the ability to hold 30 hitpoints of food, making it fourth to [[Purple sweets]], [[Saradomin brew]]s, and the [[Reward token (Gnome Restaurant)]] when it comes to the amount of hitpoints of food that can be held in one inventory slot.
